data.description: Come home to the desirable community of Montgomery Creek Ranch. Sitting on a spacious lot, this Lake Ridge Builders home boasts a premium elevation, tile flooring, faux wood blinds, and an energy efficient tankless water heater. The chef in your family will love the stunning kitchen, complete with granite countertops, a tile backsplash, 42" cabinets, and stainless steel appliances. Unwind in the spa-like master bathroom, featuring dual vanities, a 36" tub, and separate shower. Conveniently located near I-45, as well as premier shopping, dining, and entertainment at The Woodlands Mall, Market Street, Woodlands Waterway, and the Cynthia Woods Mitchell Pavilion. Schools are zoned to Conroe Independent School District. This home is perfect for creating lasting memories - call today!
